{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0a6d5aa20","title":"为印发周恩来关于中苏条约的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2bf57420c1","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":9,"articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"da244414ed","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"8f096ff24f","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1950年4月11日举行的中央人民政府委员会第六次会议。"},{"id":"439fc6c76c","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。陈，指陈云，当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。林，指林彪，当时任中央人民政府委员、中南军政委员会主席。邓，指邓小平，当时任中央人民政府委员、西南军政委员会副主席。"},{"id":"20501671c8","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张治中，当时任中央人民政府委员、西北军政委员会副主席。程潜，当时任中央人民政府委员、中南军政委员会副主席。张澜，当时任中央人民政府副主席。李济深，当时任中央人民政府副主席。黄炎培，当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。郭沫若，当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"},{"id":"d76dd8e628","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王明，即陈绍禹，当时任中央人民政府法制委员会主任委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2bd9a07bb7","type":"title","text":"为印发周恩来关于中苏条约的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"},{"id":"da244414ed","type":"paragraph","text":"此报告请周叫印若干份，于今日印好，明日分发准备参加此次中央人民政府委员会会议的一百七八十人，每人一份。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"},{"id":"8f096ff24f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"},{"id":"439fc6c76c","type":"paragraph","text":"四月九日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"},{"id":"20501671c8","type":"paragraph","text":"此次政府委员会议，除周、陈、林、邓四同志讲话外，张治中，程潜，张澜，季济深，黄炎培，郭沫若等六人似亦宜给以讲话机会，请周的定通知他们做准备。此外，为解释婚姻法，王明似亦宜略作说明","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20"}],"page":{"id":"e1bdc1d52e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"d0a6d5aa20","start":258,"end":259}}}},"__N_SSG":true}